---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="About" description="About Sunset Bridge Holdings" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>About Us</h1>
			<p>
				Here at Sunset Bridge Holdings, LLC, we are a private holding company focused
				on acquiring and operating a diversified portfolio of cash-flowing businesses
				and long-term assets.
				<br>
				We focus on building lasting value by partnering with and improving strong,
				established businesses, with an emphasis on operational strength, steady
				growth, and long-term ownership rather than short-term trading or speculation.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
